!! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
!! URxvt Appearance
!! ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
!! Font
URxvt.font:				xft:Hack:style=Regular:pixelsize=18,xft:Inconsolata Nerd Font:pixelsize=10
